nodes.text: Faime Gosan was a female Human who lived during the time of the Separatist Crisis, and was known to frequent the Outlander Club in Galactic City on Coruscant. She was seen exiting a turbolift when Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker entered the club, having tracked the bounty hunter Zam Wesell there in 22 BBY. Later, she was spotted sitting at a table opposite a Nikto.
